{
  "number": 1047,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1047",
  "title": "Ability to change the Powered By template",
  "body": "I'm handling internationalization of the search in Algolia for Zendesk right now and the string \"Search by Algolia\" is the only one I'm not able to change depending of the language.\n\nI can hack it by passing `poweredBy: false` to the widget and manually adding it myself, but I feel like we could just provide a template to replace the `PoweredBy` component on the SearchBox widget.\n",
